WEBVTT

00:01:48.425 --> 00:01:51.065
Excuse me, where does this path go?

00:01:51.585 --> 00:01:52.425
Get off me.

00:01:52.505 --> 00:01:53.545
What?

00:01:53.625 --> 00:01:54.905
Don’t touch me!

00:02:00.145 --> 00:02:02.985
What’s with the attitude?

00:02:04.985 --> 00:02:05.825
Watch out!

00:02:31.185 --> 00:02:32.345
Get away from me!

00:02:32.865 --> 00:02:34.065
Ouch!

00:02:37.625 --> 00:02:40.425
-Mister? Are you alright?
-Don’t touch me!

00:02:41.025 --> 00:02:43.265
Please calm down. I just--

00:02:43.345 --> 00:02:44.505
Go away!

00:02:45.945 --> 00:02:46.905
What?

00:02:49.745 --> 00:02:50.945
Where is he?

00:02:56.545 --> 00:02:58.385
-Hey.
-Sailom, what’s wrong?

00:02:59.025 --> 00:03:00.345
You don’t look well.

00:03:02.705 --> 00:03:04.145
I was hit by a bicycle.

00:03:04.225 --> 00:03:05.985
-What? Hit by a bicycle?
-What? Hit by a bicycle?

00:03:07.105 --> 00:03:08.665
Damn, are you alright?

00:03:09.825 --> 00:03:13.225
I’m still fine. Don’t worry.

00:03:13.305 --> 00:03:14.585
Are you sure?

00:03:22.865 --> 00:03:23.665
Oh, no!

00:03:23.745 --> 00:03:24.785
What’s wrong?

00:03:24.865 --> 00:03:25.945
My…

00:03:27.105 --> 00:03:28.025
necklace…

00:03:28.105 --> 00:03:29.305
My necklace is gone!

00:03:39.745 --> 00:03:40.905
I’ve found it!

00:03:44.105 --> 00:03:45.185
Is this yours?

00:03:51.025 --> 00:03:53.265
James, look at it.

00:03:53.345 --> 00:03:55.025
Would he wear something like that?

00:03:58.425 --> 00:04:01.465
Hey, we’ve been
searching for some time now.

00:04:01.545 --> 00:04:03.585
Did the one who hit you take it?

00:04:04.185 --> 00:04:06.065
Yeah, what does he look like?

00:04:09.385 --> 00:04:10.265
Watch out!

00:04:12.065 --> 00:04:13.145
He’s a man.

00:04:16.265 --> 00:04:17.184
Quite handsome.

00:04:19.184 --> 00:04:20.425
Not like that.

00:04:20.504 --> 00:04:24.385
Remember what makes him stand out?
Something like protruding ears,

00:04:26.185 --> 00:04:27.065
big eyes,

00:04:30.345 --> 00:04:31.185
or small eyes?

00:04:31.265 --> 00:04:33.185
Yes, I can remember!

00:04:35.585 --> 00:04:36.985
Bicycle!

00:04:40.025 --> 00:04:44.065
He rides a bicycle,
wearing a tight cycling suit!

00:04:45.225 --> 00:04:48.665
Dude…
Most people ride bicycles in Pattaya.

00:04:51.385 --> 00:04:52.505
Yep.

00:04:53.945 --> 00:04:54.905
So, what’s next?

00:05:13.785 --> 00:05:16.865
Where is that doctor who treated my wife?!

00:05:17.425 --> 00:05:19.345
-Please calm down, sir.
-Where is he?!

00:05:22.065 --> 00:05:22.905
I’ll talk to him.

00:05:24.105 --> 00:05:28.625
Damn you!
Did you tell Duean to break up with me?

00:05:28.705 --> 00:05:30.385
Mr. Kong, please calm yourself down.

00:05:30.465 --> 00:05:35.585
Why must I? My wife has been
arguing with me since she met you!

00:05:35.665 --> 00:05:37.905
I think you told her to break up with me!

00:05:37.985 --> 00:05:40.145
That’s the patient’s decision.

00:05:41.825 --> 00:05:42.705
Mr. Kong,

00:05:43.945 --> 00:05:47.345
I want you to listen
to what she really wants.

00:05:48.145 --> 00:05:49.905
You both might understand
each other better.

00:05:50.825 --> 00:05:52.105
Believe me.

00:06:05.545 --> 00:06:07.705
Are you okay?

00:06:07.785 --> 00:06:08.865
I’m fine.

00:06:13.105 --> 00:06:14.465
We’re sorry for what happened.

00:06:17.065 --> 00:06:23.065
Are you all okay? It’s been
a tough day, but we’ll get through it.

00:06:24.385 --> 00:06:25.265
Do your best.

00:06:34.305 --> 00:06:36.705
{\an8}Isn’t there any cake today?

00:06:37.865 --> 00:06:42.105
Our baker recently quit.
We’re really sorry.

00:06:42.185 --> 00:06:47.345
Then I’ll have coffee.
One hot Americano. Less sweet.

00:06:47.425 --> 00:06:48.425
Certainly.

00:06:49.065 --> 00:06:51.465
Hot Americano. Less sweet.

00:06:51.545 --> 00:06:53.505
-I'll bring it over to your table.
-Thank you.

00:07:05.665 --> 00:07:08.345
Did Nabnueng put the ring here, sweety?

00:07:08.425 --> 00:07:14.345
Yes, Mom. He said he forgot the ring
around here, but I haven’t found it.

00:07:14.425 --> 00:07:16.625
Yeah, it’s taking you a while.

00:07:17.225 --> 00:07:18.865
Have you checked between the cushions?

00:07:27.985 --> 00:07:28.905
{\an8}Mom,

00:07:31.305 --> 00:07:32.505
have you found it?

00:07:32.585 --> 00:07:35.305
No, Dear. Where did you put it?

00:07:36.585 --> 00:07:38.225
I really don’t know.

00:07:38.305 --> 00:07:41.905
It isn’t in my car or the bathroom.

00:07:42.505 --> 00:07:46.145
Bro, I couldn’t find it.
What should we do?

00:07:47.025 --> 00:07:48.865
It’s okay if you can’t find it, Looksoh.

00:07:52.225 --> 00:07:54.945
Or… did you put it in your backpack?

00:07:55.785 --> 00:07:57.505
Nope, I already checked it.

00:07:57.585 --> 00:07:59.145
Maybe you missed somewhere.

00:08:04.585 --> 00:08:07.065
Huh? What’s this…

00:08:07.705 --> 00:08:09.185
necklace?

00:08:10.985 --> 00:08:13.185
Did you buy it for Yanin?

00:08:13.265 --> 00:08:15.745
It’s beautiful. Better than the ring.

00:08:15.825 --> 00:08:19.305
Go for it, Bro.
Yanin’s gonna accept your proposal.

00:08:42.425 --> 00:08:45.585
Thank you for remembering
I wanted to try this place.

00:08:52.025 --> 00:08:53.465
-I have something to say.
-I have something to say.

00:08:56.745 --> 00:08:57.585
Go ahead.

00:09:11.345 --> 00:09:13.065
How long have we been together?

00:09:14.465 --> 00:09:15.625
It’s been a long time.

00:09:17.025 --> 00:09:17.985
Since our student days.

00:09:23.825 --> 00:09:24.985
I have something to say.

00:09:35.785 --> 00:09:38.065
Consider it bad luck.

00:09:38.145 --> 00:09:42.065
But that necklace is expensive!
My mom gave it to me!

00:09:42.145 --> 00:09:45.305
Relax. At least you weren’t hurt.

00:09:45.385 --> 00:09:46.545
This isn’t good at all!

00:09:48.185 --> 00:09:49.385
Come, let’s have a toast.

00:10:09.705 --> 00:10:11.585
Mister? Are you alright?

00:10:11.665 --> 00:10:12.585
Don’t touch me!

00:10:12.665 --> 00:10:14.025
Please calm down. I just--

00:10:14.105 --> 00:10:15.105
Go away!

00:10:30.665 --> 00:10:32.585
Wait! That’s my necklace.

00:10:32.665 --> 00:10:33.985
Huh? Where?

00:10:36.025 --> 00:10:37.985
Lemon. James. Call a guard for me.

00:10:44.385 --> 00:10:46.585
You thief! Give it back!

00:10:47.185 --> 00:10:48.025
Thief?

00:10:49.225 --> 00:10:50.345
Please mind your language.

00:10:50.425 --> 00:10:51.545
That necklace in your hand!

00:10:52.545 --> 00:10:53.545
This necklace?

00:10:54.105 --> 00:10:55.985
I saw you dropped it when we collided.

00:10:56.745 --> 00:10:58.025
So, I took it.

00:10:59.025 --> 00:11:02.985
I see. You admit you took it.

00:11:03.585 --> 00:11:05.625
What? Wait, wait.

00:11:06.305 --> 00:11:10.865
This is going too far. I shouted
for you, but you just ran away.

00:11:10.945 --> 00:11:13.425
So, I kept it to return it to you.

00:11:13.505 --> 00:11:14.465
So what?

00:11:15.825 --> 00:11:17.585
Why didn’t you give it to the police?

00:11:23.305 --> 00:11:24.585
Just know that I’m not a thief.

00:11:25.705 --> 00:11:26.985
Give my necklace back.

00:11:38.305 --> 00:11:41.105
I’m returning it to you, and that’s it.

00:11:51.865 --> 00:11:53.425
Is there a problem here?

00:11:58.025 --> 00:11:58.905
Don’t touch me.

00:11:59.665 --> 00:12:00.945
-Go away!
-What’s wrong with you?!

00:12:01.025 --> 00:12:03.025
-Are you okay, Sailom?
-Go away! Don’t touch me!

00:12:03.625 --> 00:12:04.585
-Take it easy.
-Get away from me!

00:12:08.385 --> 00:12:10.665
Please step back. I’m a doctor.

00:12:10.745 --> 00:12:13.185
Give him some space.

00:12:14.505 --> 00:12:15.345
Everyone,

00:12:17.705 --> 00:12:19.585
please step back.

00:12:19.665 --> 00:12:20.785
A little bit more.

00:12:21.465 --> 00:12:23.105
I’m a doctor. I’ll help him.

00:12:23.625 --> 00:12:24.705
Mister,

00:12:26.105 --> 00:12:27.305
please calm yourself down.

00:12:32.185 --> 00:12:33.465
Can you hear me?

00:12:46.905 --> 00:12:50.345
If you can, let’s try breathing together.

00:12:50.945 --> 00:12:55.905
Just follow me.
Breathe in, deeply and slowly.

00:12:56.945 --> 00:12:59.585
And breathe out, long and slow.

00:13:01.945 --> 00:13:03.345
Gently now.

00:13:03.425 --> 00:13:04.785
Now, place one hand…

00:13:06.025 --> 00:13:07.985
…right here on your stomach.

00:13:08.945 --> 00:13:11.105
Feel it rise as you breathe in.

00:13:15.145 --> 00:13:17.145
And feel it fall as you breathe out.

00:13:21.025 --> 00:13:23.065
Just stay with your breath.

00:13:27.385 --> 00:13:30.505
Don’t tell me you’re… a doctor.

00:13:32.985 --> 00:13:33.905
Yes, I am.

00:13:34.505 --> 00:13:35.385
Um…

00:13:36.345 --> 00:13:40.025
Don’t tell me that you’re a psychiatrist?

00:13:43.145 --> 00:13:44.105
You’re right.

00:13:46.945 --> 00:13:48.345
I’m Nabnueng.

00:13:49.425 --> 00:13:50.265
What’s your name?

00:13:51.105 --> 00:13:52.505
Sailom.

00:13:53.785 --> 00:13:54.705
I see.

00:13:55.745 --> 00:13:57.745
You handled that well for tonight.

00:13:57.825 --> 00:14:01.385
If you feel overwhelmed,
please feel free to stop by my clinic.

00:14:02.145 --> 00:14:03.745
At Term Suk - The Happiness Clinic.

00:14:05.505 --> 00:14:06.865
Thank you for your help,

00:14:08.625 --> 00:14:09.625
Doctor.

00:14:35.745 --> 00:14:39.225
Why was it okay when he touched my hand?

00:15:01.865 --> 00:15:03.225
I have something to say.

00:15:07.665 --> 00:15:09.505
-Let’s get married--
-I’m sorry.

00:15:15.465 --> 00:15:16.865
I’m so sorry.

00:15:18.225 --> 00:15:19.745
I do love you,

00:15:20.345 --> 00:15:23.385
but… I just got a new job

00:15:24.585 --> 00:15:26.305
and need to move to Vietnam.

00:15:26.905 --> 00:15:29.265
Let’s get everything sorted out first

00:15:29.345 --> 00:15:31.305
and then we can think about marriage.

00:15:33.865 --> 00:15:36.425
Hey, I’ll put lots of my photos here,

00:15:37.145 --> 00:15:40.345
so you can always think of me.

00:16:32.585 --> 00:16:34.985
How much longer? I’m in a hurry.

00:16:35.065 --> 00:16:38.345
It’s almost done. Please have a seat.

00:16:39.425 --> 00:16:42.665
It’s taking too long! I’ll miss my trip!

00:16:44.785 --> 00:16:46.865
I’ll be as quick as possible.

00:16:48.625 --> 00:16:50.425
-I'm in a bit of a hurry!
-Right away.

00:16:56.865 --> 00:16:57.865
If you like an honest person…

00:16:57.945 --> 00:17:01.425
On this day last year,

00:17:01.505 --> 00:17:04.385
a Bangkok–Chiang Mai flight

00:17:04.464 --> 00:17:08.464
crashed while landing.

00:17:08.545 --> 00:17:11.665
And sadly,

00:17:11.745 --> 00:17:15.745
a child under ten died in that accident.

00:17:15.825 --> 00:17:20.665
We’re so sorry for the child’s family.

00:17:23.505 --> 00:17:24.505
Hey there.

00:17:29.545 --> 00:17:30.665
Cheer up.

00:17:33.265 --> 00:17:35.225
It’s okay. Take your time.

00:17:35.825 --> 00:17:36.985
Thank you.

00:17:55.385 --> 00:17:57.945
This boat goes to Koh Larn!

00:17:58.625 --> 00:17:59.625
Thank you.

00:17:59.705 --> 00:18:00.585
Let's go!

00:18:00.665 --> 00:18:02.865
Thank you. All aboard!

00:18:02.945 --> 00:18:04.825
Thank you. Please board the boat.

00:18:04.905 --> 00:18:06.305
Ticket, please.

00:18:06.385 --> 00:18:07.745
Pay your debt, Dindin.

00:18:09.025 --> 00:18:11.745
Come on, I told you I’ll pay soon.

00:18:11.825 --> 00:18:13.825
Right now. Pay up.

00:18:15.425 --> 00:18:16.505
Your daughter…

00:18:17.305 --> 00:18:19.705
I must work now. I’ll pay it later.

00:18:20.305 --> 00:18:22.025
Trick me again and I’ll kill you.

00:18:22.105 --> 00:18:23.665
Don’t you see there are customers?

00:18:23.745 --> 00:18:25.065
Is this ticket for this boat?

00:18:25.145 --> 00:18:27.745
Yes, Sir. All aboard.

00:18:27.825 --> 00:18:30.105
Oh, Mister. Here’s a free hat.

00:18:31.625 --> 00:18:32.505
Can I go?

00:18:34.465 --> 00:18:36.745
Whoever has a ticket can
board the boat right away.

00:18:46.505 --> 00:18:47.905
Move forward!

00:18:47.985 --> 00:18:49.665
What? He’s gone!

00:18:50.385 --> 00:18:53.305
I told you to watch him! Damn it!

00:18:53.945 --> 00:18:55.265
He’s over there!

00:18:55.345 --> 00:18:56.585
After him!

00:19:29.025 --> 00:19:31.345
-What the hell?
-Sorry, sorry.

00:19:34.105 --> 00:19:35.065
Hey, what’s up?

00:19:35.145 --> 00:19:37.105
Can you cover for me and sing at the bar?

00:19:37.185 --> 00:19:39.785
Fine, send me the time and place.
I can only go after the transfer.

00:19:39.865 --> 00:19:41.225
-Bye.
-Hey, wait--

00:19:41.305 --> 00:19:42.185
Hey!

00:19:49.705 --> 00:19:50.825
Damn.

00:19:50.905 --> 00:19:52.385
Where the hell is he?

00:19:52.465 --> 00:19:53.585
Aish!

00:19:54.465 --> 00:19:55.705
What are we gonna do?

00:19:55.785 --> 00:19:57.425
Should we wait at his bakery?

00:19:59.145 --> 00:20:02.025
No need to go there. He’s broke anyway.

00:20:02.105 --> 00:20:04.505
Find him and squeeze the money out of him.

00:20:04.585 --> 00:20:06.265
He hasn’t even paid
the first month's interest.

00:20:06.345 --> 00:20:08.225
If the boss finds out, I’m dead.

00:20:08.305 --> 00:20:10.745
Yeah, he must be around here somewhere.

00:20:11.385 --> 00:20:12.785
Let’s check over there.

00:20:12.865 --> 00:20:14.505
Goddamn brat.

00:20:33.385 --> 00:20:35.705
BAKER NEEDED - URGENT!

00:20:37.305 --> 00:20:38.465
Bakery, huh?

00:20:52.625 --> 00:20:55.425
Pi Nabnueng, wake up!
Mom is calling you for lunch!

00:21:03.785 --> 00:21:04.745
What’s wrong?

00:21:05.785 --> 00:21:09.825
Pi Tawan, come and help me here!
Pi Nabnueng looks terrible!

00:21:12.225 --> 00:21:14.985
Look at him. Pi Nabnueng
looks like death warmed over.

00:21:20.065 --> 00:21:21.985
Are you okay, Bro?

00:21:26.145 --> 00:21:27.585
Gimme a sec to be sad.

00:21:31.665 --> 00:21:35.185
Yanin doesn’t love you, but we still do.

00:21:46.665 --> 00:21:48.225
Sleep a bit more.

00:21:48.865 --> 00:21:50.945
I’ll get some fish from
the market and grill them.

00:21:52.745 --> 00:21:55.305
Looksoh, ask Mom to get the stove ready.

00:21:55.385 --> 00:21:57.425
Yep, I’ll do it right away.

00:22:12.105 --> 00:22:13.305
I’m gonna pass you.

00:22:13.385 --> 00:22:14.785
Pass me if you can.

00:22:14.865 --> 00:22:16.585
I beat you twice already.

00:22:17.305 --> 00:22:18.465
Just zip it.

00:22:21.145 --> 00:22:23.265
Do you think I’m stopping for you?

00:22:24.305 --> 00:22:25.865
You’re slow.

00:22:25.945 --> 00:22:29.225
So what? Who threw
something at me this time?

00:22:29.305 --> 00:22:32.585
-Are you okay, Sailom?
-Go away! Don’t touch me!

00:22:33.625 --> 00:22:35.345
You need to feel the game.

00:22:35.425 --> 00:22:37.425
A little silence wouldn't kill you.

00:22:42.545 --> 00:22:44.545
I think you’re too slow, Lemon.

00:22:53.145 --> 00:22:54.345
You two…

00:22:56.425 --> 00:22:57.665
About last night…

00:22:59.025 --> 00:23:00.065
I’m so sorry.

00:23:09.105 --> 00:23:10.545
It’s okay.

00:23:11.665 --> 00:23:13.945
But why were you like that last night?

00:23:14.785 --> 00:23:18.505
Yeah, you can tell us your problems.

00:23:24.785 --> 00:23:26.145
Thanks a lot…

00:23:26.985 --> 00:23:29.665
but… I’m fine, really.

00:23:33.105 --> 00:23:34.225
Sailom…

00:23:41.705 --> 00:23:45.425
We understand if
you don’t want to tell us.

00:23:45.505 --> 00:23:49.545
We just want to understand you better,

00:23:49.625 --> 00:23:53.105
so we know what’s okay and what’s not.

00:23:57.865 --> 00:23:59.345
Sorry.

00:24:01.825 --> 00:24:03.545
I’m not ready to talk about it.

00:24:07.665 --> 00:24:11.425
Hey, didn’t you invite us to eat?
I’m starving.

00:24:11.505 --> 00:24:15.945
When will you order some food?
Or should I eat the table legs?

00:24:19.185 --> 00:24:21.265
What’s so funny? Order something.

00:24:21.345 --> 00:24:25.305
Okay, I’ll do it.
If you’re in a hurry, do it yourself.

00:24:36.785 --> 00:24:41.185
Fresh seafood here. Come and get it.

00:24:41.265 --> 00:24:44.985
Live fish and crabs right here.
Want some, handsome?

00:24:45.865 --> 00:24:47.385
How much for a kilo of squid?

00:24:47.465 --> 00:24:49.305
300 baht per kilo. How many kilos?

00:24:50.745 --> 00:24:53.025
-Is this all that’s left?
-Yes, just three left.

00:24:53.105 --> 00:24:55.545
-I’ll take all three.
-Alright.

00:24:56.425 --> 00:24:57.585
Anything else?

00:24:58.345 --> 00:25:00.465
-Just squid.
-Alright.

00:25:01.145 --> 00:25:02.465
Look at these squid.

00:25:02.545 --> 00:25:04.225
Oh! many shelfish.

00:25:04.985 --> 00:25:06.345
Shellfish are fresh here.

00:25:06.945 --> 00:25:08.465
Oh, Captain.

00:25:09.105 --> 00:25:10.865
How do you do?

00:25:13.905 --> 00:25:15.745
Yes, I’m okay.

00:25:16.265 --> 00:25:19.265
I heard you’re not flying anymore.

00:25:20.625 --> 00:25:22.865
Yes, I’m not.

00:25:27.625 --> 00:25:28.945
How have you been?

00:25:29.025 --> 00:25:35.545
After that day, my husband and I
moved here to Pattaya to run a business.

00:25:40.745 --> 00:25:42.265
I’m truly sorry.

00:25:44.105 --> 00:25:45.625
It’s okay.

00:25:46.465 --> 00:25:48.545
I’m not here to blame you.

00:25:56.665 --> 00:25:57.505
Dear…

00:25:58.505 --> 00:25:59.785
Look there.

00:26:00.385 --> 00:26:02.545
The captain likes squid

00:26:02.625 --> 00:26:04.345
just like our daughter used to.

00:26:26.705 --> 00:26:27.745
Here.

00:26:29.625 --> 00:26:30.625
Thanks.

00:26:48.305 --> 00:26:49.145
Hey.

00:26:50.385 --> 00:26:51.225
Why are you spacing out?

00:26:52.185 --> 00:26:53.025
Nothing.

00:26:58.025 --> 00:26:59.345
Where’s Sky?

00:27:00.505 --> 00:27:01.905
Working, maybe?

00:27:05.265 --> 00:27:08.425
He’s been busy lately.
Been out since this morning.

00:27:09.025 --> 00:27:10.065
Meeting with customers.

00:27:25.345 --> 00:27:26.465
Feel better, Dear?

00:27:29.225 --> 00:27:30.225
Yes, Mom.

00:27:31.865 --> 00:27:36.705
That’s life. Nothing’s certain at all.

00:27:39.105 --> 00:27:40.025
You’re right.

00:27:40.705 --> 00:27:43.825
Still heartbroken, Bro?

00:27:44.705 --> 00:27:45.705
Yep.

00:27:46.625 --> 00:27:49.545
Now I get what it feels like to be dumped.

00:27:52.065 --> 00:27:53.985
She’s been stringing
you along all this time.

00:27:55.865 --> 00:27:56.905
I know.

00:28:00.145 --> 00:28:02.065
But when seeing it for myself…

00:28:04.025 --> 00:28:05.145
I’m just lost.

00:28:07.985 --> 00:28:11.905
Yeah… give it some time, Doctor.

00:28:17.425 --> 00:28:19.625
Even a psychiatrist needs his mom’s care.

00:28:20.785 --> 00:28:24.825
Look who’s talking, Tawan.
Don’t think I don’t know.

00:28:24.905 --> 00:28:29.345
It’s okay to tell me if something’s
upsetting you. Don’t be shy.

00:28:30.105 --> 00:28:32.425
What? I’m fine!

00:28:32.505 --> 00:28:33.465
Yeah, right.

00:28:36.665 --> 00:28:38.345
Alright, let’s have a toast!

00:28:38.425 --> 00:28:39.865
Come on!

00:28:41.105 --> 00:28:43.385
Okay, cheers!

00:28:45.025 --> 00:28:46.665
Bottoms up, shall we?

00:28:49.185 --> 00:28:51.945
-Are you sure, Mom?
-Look at your brother.

00:29:01.345 --> 00:29:02.425
I’m sorry…

00:29:04.905 --> 00:29:06.785
I couldn’t help you at all.

00:29:24.025 --> 00:29:24.865
Hey, Ben.

00:29:25.385 --> 00:29:28.625
I almost got my ass kicked
by the debt collectors today.

00:29:29.665 --> 00:29:30.865
They were hunting me down.

00:29:31.665 --> 00:29:34.305
Didn’t you say
you would transfer the money today?

00:29:35.025 --> 00:29:39.985
Don't give me that crap! I saw your IG!
You took a girl out for omakase!

00:29:41.745 --> 00:29:47.025
Borrowing was easy for you.
Don't make returning it so damn hard.

00:29:47.625 --> 00:29:50.665
Send me the money now,
or you’ll deal with me.

00:29:52.265 --> 00:29:53.105
Ben?

00:29:54.185 --> 00:29:55.025
Hello?

00:29:55.945 --> 00:29:57.545
You bastard.

00:30:04.265 --> 00:30:05.505
Damn it!

00:30:05.585 --> 00:30:07.145
Ouch! Who did this?!

00:30:08.625 --> 00:30:09.665
Was it you?

00:30:11.265 --> 00:30:12.185
What’s your problem?

00:30:13.505 --> 00:30:15.225
What the hell is wrong with you?

00:30:16.105 --> 00:30:17.025
You brat.

00:30:20.145 --> 00:30:22.425
Bastard.

00:30:23.345 --> 00:30:24.225
You started it.

00:30:24.945 --> 00:30:25.985
You want a piece of me?

00:30:26.065 --> 00:30:28.505
-What if I do?
-Take this.

00:30:42.625 --> 00:30:43.465
Fine.

00:31:27.385 --> 00:31:29.345
Does it have to be this early, Mom?

00:31:30.425 --> 00:31:32.905
Keeping busy is good.

00:31:32.985 --> 00:31:35.425
It’ll help take
your mind off your heartbreak.

00:31:36.625 --> 00:31:38.905
I’m not that heartbroken.

00:31:38.985 --> 00:31:41.345
This is the best way.

00:31:41.425 --> 00:31:43.345
Here, deliver this drink.

00:31:43.425 --> 00:31:45.185
I’ve sent you the address.

00:31:47.705 --> 00:31:48.825
It’s not that far.

00:31:49.345 --> 00:31:52.345
Yes, now hurry, or it’ll get cold.

00:31:53.025 --> 00:31:54.425
-Okay, Mom.
-See you.

00:32:18.065 --> 00:32:19.745
How long will you be
in Chiangmai this time?

00:32:20.345 --> 00:32:22.625
Maybe a week?

00:32:23.545 --> 00:32:24.945
I’ll buy sai oua for you.

00:32:25.705 --> 00:32:26.545
Okay.

00:32:26.625 --> 00:32:28.305
Have a safe trip, Dad.

00:32:28.825 --> 00:32:30.185
Call me when you’re there.

00:32:30.745 --> 00:32:31.785
Of course.

00:32:52.425 --> 00:32:53.985
Yes, Mom?

00:32:54.705 --> 00:32:58.505
How’s everything in Pattaya?
Are you doing okay?

00:33:00.465 --> 00:33:01.825
I’m good, Mom.

00:33:01.905 --> 00:33:05.265
You’re alright staying by yourself?

00:33:06.905 --> 00:33:09.025
Of course, Mom.

00:33:09.105 --> 00:33:10.305
But…

00:33:10.385 --> 00:33:11.585
Mom…

00:33:12.305 --> 00:33:17.905
don’t worry. I’m grown up now.
I can take care of myself.

00:33:17.985 --> 00:33:23.665
Right. If there’s something wrong,
you can call me anytime. Okay?

00:33:23.745 --> 00:33:24.865
Alright.

00:33:25.465 --> 00:33:26.745
I gotta go.

00:33:26.825 --> 00:33:28.905
Okay. I love you, Dear.

00:33:28.985 --> 00:33:30.745
I love you too, Mom.

00:33:39.745 --> 00:33:41.345
Hello!

00:33:41.425 --> 00:33:42.985
"Love Like a Bike" delivery here.

00:33:51.825 --> 00:33:53.385
Oh, Doctor.

00:33:54.025 --> 00:33:55.185
Oh, Sailom.

00:33:56.985 --> 00:34:02.065
You’re a doctor. Buy why…
are you delivering coffee?

00:34:03.225 --> 00:34:06.945
Oh, it’s my family’s café.
I help out at the café after my day job.

00:34:07.705 --> 00:34:09.105
Here’s your coffee.

00:34:09.744 --> 00:34:10.824
The payment’s been processed.

00:34:11.425 --> 00:34:12.625
Okay, thank you.

00:34:19.264 --> 00:34:21.025
Go away! Don’t touch me!

00:34:21.824 --> 00:34:23.145
Why was it okay…

00:34:25.145 --> 00:34:27.344
when he touched my hand?

00:34:38.905 --> 00:34:40.945
Don’t hurt me! Mom, help me!

00:34:41.025 --> 00:34:42.865
Silent!

00:34:44.625 --> 00:34:45.465
No!

00:34:47.185 --> 00:34:48.505
Don’t hurt me.

00:34:49.905 --> 00:34:50.985
Get out!

00:34:57.705 --> 00:34:58.665
Sailom.

00:35:02.105 --> 00:35:03.265
It’s okay.

00:35:03.785 --> 00:35:05.265
Stay with me.

00:35:08.105 --> 00:35:09.505
Breathe in deeply.

00:35:28.545 --> 00:35:30.825
I’m… sorry.

00:35:33.665 --> 00:35:35.225
It’s totally fine.

00:36:00.465 --> 00:36:01.625
Oh.

00:36:01.705 --> 00:36:02.585
Sailom.

00:36:04.785 --> 00:36:06.465
Put this shirt on quickly.

00:36:08.105 --> 00:36:08.945
Thank you.

00:36:24.825 --> 00:36:29.345
By the way, I ordered you new coffee.
I'll bring it over to you soon.

00:36:29.425 --> 00:36:31.665
It’s okay. I spilled it.

00:36:32.425 --> 00:36:33.465
Well…

00:36:33.545 --> 00:36:35.345
I’ll wash and return your shirt later.

00:36:35.425 --> 00:36:37.905
Don’t worry. I can wash it myself.

00:36:37.985 --> 00:36:40.225
Please, I insist.

00:36:40.305 --> 00:36:41.505
It’s totally fine.

00:36:41.585 --> 00:36:42.905
It’s really okay.

00:36:44.585 --> 00:36:46.305
Don’t you have other places to deliver?

00:36:47.105 --> 00:36:48.145
There are no orders now.

00:36:55.265 --> 00:36:56.705
Can I ask you?

00:36:58.105 --> 00:36:59.505
How many jobs do you have?

00:37:00.625 --> 00:37:04.985
Not many. Just the clinic and the café.

00:37:07.825 --> 00:37:10.265
Feel free to visit the café.

00:37:10.905 --> 00:37:11.905
Coffee’s on me.

00:37:18.465 --> 00:37:20.905
I’ll borrow your pen.

00:37:45.465 --> 00:37:47.185
Thank you, Doctor.

00:37:47.945 --> 00:37:48.905
You’re welcome.

00:38:00.225 --> 00:38:01.385
Yes, Mom?

00:38:01.465 --> 00:38:05.145
Nabnueng,
can you deliver another cup for me?

00:38:05.225 --> 00:38:06.625
Right away, Mom.

00:38:09.105 --> 00:38:11.705
-I've got to go now.
-Alright.

00:38:33.465 --> 00:38:36.345
It reeks of coffee now.

00:38:37.505 --> 00:38:38.945
Can I get this stain out?

00:38:48.145 --> 00:38:50.065
Hey. You can’t be serious.

00:38:50.665 --> 00:38:54.425
There are many places to go in Pattaya,
but you chose to come here?

00:38:54.505 --> 00:38:56.985
Don’t they have cafés in the US?

00:38:57.065 --> 00:38:59.585
I just got back. Spoil me a little.

00:38:59.665 --> 00:39:03.225
Don’t you want to chill out on an island?

00:39:04.185 --> 00:39:07.705
We can go later. The summer’s long anyway.

00:39:09.985 --> 00:39:11.425
Here’s your receipt.

00:39:12.945 --> 00:39:13.985
Thank you.

00:39:15.985 --> 00:39:18.865
Are you on vacation?
I’ve never seen you before.

00:39:18.945 --> 00:39:21.705
I'm a local,
but this is my first time here.

00:39:21.785 --> 00:39:25.705
My friend just came back
from the US and brought us here.

00:39:26.825 --> 00:39:28.505
Did you read reviews from somewhere?

00:39:29.105 --> 00:39:30.105
Not at all.

00:39:30.985 --> 00:39:32.785
I only want to use this.

00:39:33.985 --> 00:39:35.025
Here.

00:39:39.305 --> 00:39:40.625
you’re Pi Sailom, right?

00:39:41.225 --> 00:39:43.785
Pi Nabnueng mentioned you.
Everything’s on the house today.

00:39:43.865 --> 00:39:46.425
Just a cup of coffee is enough.

00:39:46.505 --> 00:39:47.705
I can pay for the rest.

00:39:47.785 --> 00:39:50.505
Don’t worry.
Pi Nabnueng said you all can eat for free.

00:39:57.105 --> 00:40:00.105
Tell Doctor Nabnueng
that I said "thank you."

00:40:00.185 --> 00:40:01.265
Yes.

00:40:03.865 --> 00:40:05.065
Isn’t…

00:40:05.145 --> 00:40:06.545
Doctor Nabnueng here?

00:40:06.625 --> 00:40:10.185
He works at his clinic today.
It’s not far from here.

00:40:10.265 --> 00:40:11.905
I see…

00:40:13.185 --> 00:40:16.585
Please stop by tomorrow.
We’ll have baked goods again.

00:40:17.385 --> 00:40:18.305
Alright.

00:40:19.305 --> 00:40:21.625
Excuse me, can I have a menu?

00:40:24.185 --> 00:40:29.425
Wait. Doctor Nabnueng?
Is he the guy you took your necklace from?

00:40:29.505 --> 00:40:30.985
When did you get close to him?

00:40:35.665 --> 00:40:37.825
Come on. Let’s go somewhere else.

00:40:56.985 --> 00:41:00.425
Let’s split up here.
I’ve got something to do.

00:41:00.505 --> 00:41:01.585
Wait…

00:41:01.665 --> 00:41:03.425
What’s this?

00:41:03.505 --> 00:41:08.105
You invited us here, then want to leave,
and now you’ve got something to do?

00:41:08.185 --> 00:41:09.105
You’re suspicious.

00:41:11.825 --> 00:41:13.025
It’s nothing much!

00:41:13.985 --> 00:41:17.385
I just wanted you two to try coffee here.

00:41:18.505 --> 00:41:20.905
How did you get that name card?

00:41:20.985 --> 00:41:25.225
When did you get close to that doctor?
Didn’t you two fight that night?

00:41:26.905 --> 00:41:28.225
His name is Nabnueng!

00:41:28.825 --> 00:41:31.065
I asked when you two got close.

00:41:33.745 --> 00:41:34.625
Well…

00:41:35.505 --> 00:41:36.825
not that close.

00:41:37.545 --> 00:41:43.065
Yesterday, Doctor Nabnueng delivered
coffee to my house and I spilled it.

00:41:43.745 --> 00:41:49.585
He gave me the card with his
signature to make up for it. That’s all.

00:41:50.745 --> 00:41:52.065
-Really?!
-Really?!

00:41:53.105 --> 00:41:53.945
Yep!

00:41:54.985 --> 00:41:56.465
Do you like him?

00:41:57.665 --> 00:42:00.825
Come on! I only just met him!

00:42:00.905 --> 00:42:02.585
It’s love at first sight.

00:42:04.945 --> 00:42:07.105
I’m done talking with you guys.

00:42:07.945 --> 00:42:09.145
-I am out there.
-What?

00:42:12.105 --> 00:42:14.025
What’s next?

00:42:14.105 --> 00:42:16.625
Let's just go home. Your house, my house.

00:42:17.425 --> 00:42:18.905
-Come.
-Okay.

00:42:27.825 --> 00:42:30.905
Mom, I have some gossip.

00:42:30.985 --> 00:42:33.385
THIS MAN CAN HAVE EVERYTHING FOR FREE.
FROM DOCTOR NABNUENG.

00:42:34.505 --> 00:42:36.705
Oh, who’s this?

00:42:36.785 --> 00:42:41.225
He’s Pi Sailom from the US.
Pi Nabnueng can finally move on.

00:42:41.945 --> 00:42:44.625
-Isn’t it too soon?
-Not at all.

00:42:46.705 --> 00:42:48.865
I’d better text Pi Nabnueng

00:42:49.705 --> 00:42:50.665
Mom,

00:42:51.425 --> 00:42:54.465
when is the 'yummy treat' baker coming?

00:42:56.025 --> 00:42:57.545
He’ll be here soon.

00:43:00.345 --> 00:43:01.345
Good afternoon, Mrs. Phailin.

00:43:01.425 --> 00:43:03.425
Oh, Dindin. You’re here.

00:43:04.185 --> 00:43:06.665
I prepared the ingredients.
Let’s get started.

00:43:06.745 --> 00:43:08.305
Yes, right away.

00:43:09.185 --> 00:43:12.305
Tawan! Come here!

00:43:12.385 --> 00:43:13.705
What is it, Mom?

00:43:30.905 --> 00:43:32.225
You brat.

00:43:33.545 --> 00:43:34.385
You started it.

00:43:34.465 --> 00:43:35.345
You want a piece of me?

00:43:35.425 --> 00:43:37.065
What if I do?

00:43:42.905 --> 00:43:45.305
Good afternoon, Pi Tawan.

00:44:21.345 --> 00:44:24.625
Hello. Do you have an appointment?

00:44:25.505 --> 00:44:27.705
Ah, no…I don’t.

00:44:28.545 --> 00:44:30.385
I’m actually here to see Dr. Nubnueng

00:44:31.065 --> 00:44:32.385
Oh,

00:44:32.465 --> 00:44:36.425
he’s out for field work today.

00:44:36.505 --> 00:44:38.625
-Field work?
-Yes.

00:45:02.105 --> 00:45:03.105
Sailom?

00:45:05.945 --> 00:45:07.145
What brings you here?

00:45:09.025 --> 00:45:13.145
Oh… I was just passing by.

00:45:14.385 --> 00:45:17.625
What about you? What are you doing here?

00:45:19.465 --> 00:45:21.705
I’m out doing field work
with the SWING Foundation.

00:45:22.345 --> 00:45:24.905
Providing
counseling for nightlife workers.

00:45:24.985 --> 00:45:27.905
They deserve the same
protections as everyone else.

00:45:28.905 --> 00:45:30.105
I see.

00:45:30.785 --> 00:45:34.025
I thought you only
saw patients at the clinic.

00:45:34.105 --> 00:45:35.585
I didn’t expect to see you out here.

00:45:36.465 --> 00:45:38.265
I just want to help out however I can.

00:45:43.545 --> 00:45:44.385
Are you hungry?

00:45:45.385 --> 00:45:46.225
Huh?

00:45:47.105 --> 00:45:49.585
-Hungry for what?
-Hungry for dinner.

00:45:49.665 --> 00:45:51.185
Want to go grab a bite?

00:46:13.825 --> 00:46:15.345
{\an8}Take it slow, or you’ll get drunk.

00:46:15.425 --> 00:46:16.705
{\an8}I’m fine, Doc.

00:46:17.345 --> 00:46:18.665
{\an8}I can handle this much.

00:46:18.745 --> 00:46:22.665
{\an8}This is my first time.
Didn’t know it’d… feel this good.

00:46:22.745 --> 00:46:25.025
{\an8}-Do you like it?
-I do.

00:46:26.225 --> 00:46:29.585
{\an8}Seriously, have you ever
baked before? I don’t think you have.

00:46:29.665 --> 00:46:32.145
{\an8}If you’re an expert, do it yourself.

00:46:32.745 --> 00:46:33.585
{\an8}Oh, no…

00:46:34.705 --> 00:46:36.985
{\an8}Don’t tell me the Doctor…